
The files contained here are the affiliations for the mud.

Note the following set fns to be used.

set_affiliation_sponsor(string str);
	This is used when a deity/god looks after the affiliation.
	these are gods in the RP sense (not admin or actual people).
	This is used for spell combat messages only)

set_affiliation_name(string name);
	The actual NAME of the affiliation, like followers of the
	All-God, or some such hting.

set_affiliation_file(string filename);
	All affiliation files (objects) go into the dir /obj/skills/affils
	The file u type here is the abreviated file name, which is also used
	as the affiliations channel (like, e.g. 'wrm')

